Performance Index Categories:
- High: Average goals scored greater than 1.5 and win rate greater than 0.5;
- Medium-High: Average goals scored between 1.0 and 1.5 (inclusive) and win rate greater than 0.5;
- Medium-Low: Average goals scored between 0.5 and 1.0 (inclusive) and win rate greater than 0.5;
- Low: All other cases.
